Params: {1: 'Nona Ouroboros', 2: 'Chapter 11', 3: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Atlas/CommonLogo/BgLogo1.png'}
{1: 'ThemeEnable'}
{1: 'Assets/Product/Texture/Image/BgStory/Bgstory121.png'}
{3: 'Asslam, Carriage 014'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Sophia and I searched every carriage and every possible hiding place.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Sophia', 3: '...Including the 64 ventilation pipes and 7 garbage disposal points. Nothing found.', 4: '3'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: '...No signs or traces of Commandant.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Liv, did the radar pick anything up?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "Cannot determine exact coordinates. Someone is interfering with Commandant's signals...", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Liv', 3: "Lee is trying to locate and neutralize the source of the interference, but they're very good at hiding...", 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: 'The signal is perfectly disguised. Whoever is doing it must be very familiar with how our radar positioning systems work.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: "Let's note that down first. Right now, our priority is to locate Commandant. Lee, how long do you need to decode the signal?", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'Ten minutes, or less.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Sophia', 3: "...I'll go report to Jamilah.", 4: '2'}
{3: "As if following Sophia's words, two sets of footsteps sound from the distance."}
{1: '1', 2: 'Aston', 3: 'Let us not disturb Amir, Sophia.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Aston', 3: 'Amir has important matters to tend to.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Aston', 3: "The mechanic patrols told us what happened. It is Akdilek's fault for not taking better care of its guest aboard Asslam.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Aston', 3: 'We will do all we can to help find your commandant.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Aston', 3: 'By the way, may I inquire as to the whereabouts of Miss Bianca? Could it be possible that she and your commandant left on some urgent business?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Commandant would never leave us without notice. As for Bianca, she returned to Babylonia yesterday for another mission.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: "So Bianca's departure does not coincide with the time Commandant went missing.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Changyu', 3: "...It wouldn't be those rebels, would it? That damn Ashlar's vanished as well.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Liv', 3: "The signals from Commandant's Mind Beacon is fading...", 4: '2'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: 'Calm your M.I.N.D., Liv.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'All of you are registering a 4.275% M.I.N.D. deviation. Try to stabilize your emotion modules.', 4: '3'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Changyu', 3: 'Wait, do you smell something...?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Changyu', 3: 'Where did you last see 【kuroname】?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Changyu', 3: "Akdilek stores all kinds of spices for trade. You foreigners can't tell the smell apart, but I can... and I'm all too familiar with this scent.", 4: '1'}
{2: 'Changyu', 3: "...It's the smell of a knockout drug.", 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lee', 3: '...Methoxyflurane and other chemical substances detected in the air.', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Changyu', 3: 'Effective on humans but not on Constructs—a simple, yet cunning trick... Those psycho boaters are finally sticking their oars here, huh...', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Aston', 3: 'What do you mean, Changyu?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Changyu', 3: 'I\'m afraid your Commandant got "bought", much like how I got sold to this place.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Changyu', 3: 'But how did those collared get off their ship...?', 4: '1'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Lucia', 3: 'What are you talking about, Changyu?', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: '...Interference cleared. Commandant located. The signal is moving toward the port of City 09.', 4: '2'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'I tried to pull up info about the city from the database, but I don\'t have the clearance. Only the names "Citong Port"" and ""Kowloong Chamber of Commerce" showed up.', 4: '2'}
{1: '1', 2: 'Changyu', 3: '...The KCC. I knew it was that ship.', 4: '1'}
{2: 'Changyu', 3: "Looks like you're in big trouble, Gray Raven.", 4: '1'}
